OL,3,C'The truth has come out' - former sub
OL,4,Cpostmaster says scandal ruined his life
OL,6,FA former sub-postmaster from southeast
OL,7,FLondon says "the truth has come out"
OL,8,Ffollowing a damning report into the
OL,9,FPost Office Horizon IT scandal.
OL,11,FParmod Kalia ran a Post Office Branch
OL,12,Fin Orpington in Kent for over a decade
OL,13,Fwhen he was wrongly accused of theft
OL,14,Fin 2001.
OL,16,FThe father of four was sentenced to
OL,17,Fsix months in prison and used #22,000
OL,18,Fof his mother's life savings pay to
OL,19,Fthe Post Office despite there being no
OL,20,Fproof he stole it.
