OL,3,C'The truth has come out' - former sub
OL,4,Cpostmaster says scandal ruined his life
OL,6,FHe's just one of approximately 1,000
OL,7,Fsub postmasters between 1999 and 2015
OL,8,Fwho were prosecuted after faulty
OL,9,FHorizon accounting software made it
OL,10,Flook as though money was missing from
OL,11,Ftheir accounts.
OL,13,FAnd, one of 93 people who had their
OL,14,Fconvictions overturned.
