OL,3,C'The truth has come out' - former sub
OL,4,Cpostmaster says scandal ruined his life
OL,6,FA first tranche of the public
OL,7,Finquiry's final report into the
OL,8,Fscandal, published on Tuesday, laid
OL,9,Fbare the devastating consequences for
OL,10,Fvictims and their families, from
OL,11,Fpolice investigations to convictions
OL,12,Fand imprisonment.
OL,14,FSpeaking about his experience, Mr
OL,15,FKalia said it's shaved years off his
OL,16,Flife and left his family questioning
OL,17,Fif he had stolen thousands of pounds
OL,18,Ffrom the Post Office until they found
OL,19,Fan answer.
