OL,3,C'The truth has come out' - former sub
OL,4,Cpostmaster says scandal ruined his life
OL,6,FMr Kalia said: "No matter how many
OL,7,Fnoughts they're going to put on (the
OL,8,Fcompensation), the end of it is not
OL,9,Fgoing to sort out my life, the lost
OL,10,Flife of 25 years with family, friends
OL,11,Fand health.
OL,13,F"From 2001 to 2015, other than
OL,14,Farguments at home, the children
OL,15,Fdoubting me saying 'have you taken
OL,16,Fit?' I had no answers because I didn't
OL,17,Fsuspect it was a computer system.
