OL,3,C'The truth has come out' - former sub
OL,4,Cpostmaster says scandal ruined his life
OL,6,F"I had no idea it was a computer
OL,7,Fsystem until 2015 when I saw the BBC
OL,8,FPanorama programme and that's when I
OL,9,Frealised there were problems at the
OL,10,FPost Office.
OL,12,F"I wrote a letter to the then CEO
OL,13,FPaula Vennels, saying, I think this is
OL,14,Fwhat's possibly happened at my office,
OL,15,Fcould you please open my file and have
OL,16,Fa look?
OL,18,F"The answer I got back in 2015 was no,
OL,19,Fthere's nothing wrong with the system.
