OL,3,C'The truth has come out' - former sub
OL,4,Cpostmaster says scandal ruined his life
OL,6,F"I'm relieved now that the truth has
OL,7,Fcome out.
OL,9,F"People do realise and understand that
OL,10,Fthere were problems and faults in Post
OL,11,FOffice, but they were just covering it
OL,12,Fup all along, which was apparent at
OL,13,Fthe inquiry.
OL,15,F"But now the judge, Sir Wyn Williams
OL,16,Fhas actually put it in writing. The
OL,17,Freport is very critical of the Post
OL,18,FOffice and the government as to in
OL,19,Ftheir handling of any redress that
OL,20,Fthey're going to do.
