OL,3,C'The truth has come out' - former sub
OL,4,Cpostmaster says scandal ruined his life
OL,6,F"It's a total mess up the schemes and
OL,7,Fhopefully Sir Wyn Williams is now
OL,8,Fgoing to rectify all of that as well."
OL,10,FMr Kalia also praised other sub
OL,11,Fpostmasters and said he wouldn't be
OL,12,Fwhere he is now without the support
OL,13,Ffrom other sub-postmasters.
OL,15,FTuesday's 162-page report, written by
OL,16,Finquiry chair Sir Wyn Williams, also
OL,17,Fconcluded Post Office bosses knew the
OL,18,FHorizon IT system had widespread
OL,19,Ffaults, but had "maintained the
OL,20,Ffiction" it was accurate for years.
