OL,3,C'The truth has come out' - former sub
OL,4,Cpostmaster says scandal ruined his life
OL,6,FThe report also found the Legacy
OL,7,FHorizon system's 2010 replacement -
OL,8,Fknown as Horizon Online - was also
OL,9,F"afflicted by bugs" and that employees
OL,10,Fof Fujitsu and the Post Office "knew
OL,11,Fthat this was so".
OL,13,FThe inquiry estimates that as many as
OL,14,F10,000 people may have been affected
OL,15,Fby the Horizon scandal, including both
OL,16,Fconvicted sub postmasters and those
OL,17,Fwho experienced financial or
OL,18,Freputational damage as a result of the
OL,19,Fsystem's failures.
