OL,3,C'The truth has come out' - former sub
OL,4,Cpostmaster says scandal ruined his life
OL,6,FThe report said 59 victims of the
OL,7,Fscandal contemplated suicide with 10
OL,8,Fattempting to take their own lives.
OL,10,FInquiry chairman Sir Wyn Williams said
OL,11,Fthere was a "real possibility" 13
OL,12,Fpeople took their own lives as a
OL,13,Fresult of the suffering they endured
OL,14,Fduring the scandal.
OL,16,FOther details in the report detailed
OL,17,Fimpacts including bankruptcy and
OL,18,Frelationship breakdowns.
