OL,3,C'The truth has come out' - former sub
OL,4,Cpostmaster says scandal ruined his life
OL,6,FMr Kalia said he wants the see the
OL,7,FPost Office, staff at Fujitsu and all
OL,8,Fthose who knew "acknowledge and accept
OL,9,Fthat they had done wrong, not only to
OL,10,Fthe postmasters but the families.
OL,12,F"The families have had a big knock on
OL,13,Feffect whether it's as children,
OL,14,Fwhether it's my mother, who's now
OL,15,Factually passed away, who gave me her
OL,16,Fmoney and I haven't been able to give
OL,17,Fit back to her."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/14
