OL,3,C'The truth has come out' - former sub
OL,4,Cpostmaster says scandal ruined his life
OL,6,F"My family members, my children have
OL,7,Fgone through trauma to such an extent
OL,8,Fthat even now they're adults
OL,9,Fthemselves, they're still seeking
OL,10,Fcounselling as to what happened.
OL,12,F"The whole family was actually
OL,13,Fdescribed by my children as a
OL,14,Fdysfunctional family at the time.
OL,16,F"It hurt. I'm a father, I'm supposed
OL,17,Fto look after them, I'm supposed to be
OL,18,Ftaking care of them but I was not able
OL,19,Fto.
OL,21,F"I was sent to prison."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/14
