OL,3,C'The truth has come out' - former sub
OL,4,Cpostmaster says scandal ruined his life
OL,6,F"Acceptance is the first step of
OL,7,Ftrying to put matters right, which
OL,8,Fthey still haven't done. They've given
OL,9,Fmealy mouth apologies which mean
OL,10,Fnothing to nobody."
OL,12,FMr Kalia has not yet been given
OL,13,Fcompensation after the decision to
OL,14,Fconvict him was overturned in May 2021.
OL,16,FA Post Office spokesperson said: "The
OL,17,FInquiry has brought to life the
OL,18,Fdevastating stories of those impacted
OL,19,Fby the Horizon Scandal. Their
OL,20,Fexperiences represent a shameful
OL,21,Fperiod in our history.
