OL,3,C'The truth has come out' - former sub
OL,4,Cpostmaster says scandal ruined his life
OL,6,F"We must never lose sight of the
OL,7,FHorizon Scandal's human impact on
OL,8,Fpostmasters and their families, which
OL,9,Fthe Inquiry has highlighted so well.
OL,11,F"Sir Wyn's report highlights a series
OL,12,Fof failings by the Post Office and
OL,13,Fvarious governments. His
OL,14,Frecommendations are immensely helpful
OL,15,Fas a guide for what is needed to
OL,16,Ffinish the job, and we will respond in
OL,17,Ffull to Parliament after carefully
OL,18,Fconsidering them."
